flowchart TD
    A[User clicks Run] --> B{Detect runnable file}
    B -->|index.html| C[Open in new browser tab]
    B -->|main.py / app.py| D[Spawn subprocess]
    D --> E[Poll stdout every 500ms]
    E --> F{Process running?}
    F -->|Yes| G[Display output in console]
    G --> H{User types input?}
    H -->|Yes| I[Send to stdin pipe]
    I --> E
    H -->|No| E
    F -->|Exited| J[Show exit code]
    F -->|User clicks Stop| K[Send CTRL_BREAK / terminate]
    K --> J

    L[User opens git history] --> M[Display commit timeline]
    M --> N{User action per commit}
    N -->|Reset| O[Checkout files at commit]
    O --> P[New commit recorded]
    N -->|Branch| Q[Copy files at commit to new folder]
    Q --> R[New chat with ancestor history]
    N -->|Run| S[Extract files to temp directory]
    S --> T[Run in temp dir with polling]
    T --> U[Auto-cleanup on stop/exit]
